---
/**
 * Labels / Interface Texte Editor Card
 * The grid for labels is populated by JS (renderLabelsForm).
 */
---

<div class="admin-card mb-8">
  <div class="admin-card-header">
    <div>
      <div class="admin-card-title">Interface Texte</div>
      <div class="admin-card-subtitle">Labels, Navigation &amp; CTAs</div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <button onclick="loadLabelsArea()" class="admin-btn admin-btn-ghost text-xs">Daten laden</button>
      <button id="toggle-labels-btn"
              class="admin-btn admin-btn-secondary text-xs flex items-center gap-x-1.5 px-3 py-1.5">
        <span id="toggle-labels-label">Ausklappen</span>
        <svg id="toggle-labels-chevron" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="labels-editor-content" style="max-height:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;">
    <div class="admin-card-body">
      <p class="admin-help mb-4">
        Hier kannst du alle sichtbaren Texte der Website anpassen (Navigation, Labels, Buttons, Byline usw.). 
        Nach dem Speichern werden die Änderungen über den Workflow live geschaltet.
      </p>
      <div id="labels-editor" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-7 gap-y-5">
        <!-- JS populated premium inputs with gold borders, matching Speisekarten editor -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="admin-card-footer">
      <button onclick="saveLabelsArea()" class="admin-btn admin-btn-primary">Labels speichern</button>
      <div id="labels-status" class="admin-status flex-1"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
